observer
Class WorkspaceMessage

java.lang.Object
  observer.WorkspaceMessage

public class WorkspaceMessage
extends java.lang.Object

Message sent by WorkspacePublishers to classes that implement WorkspaceSubscriber i.e. that subscribe to change notifications from a workspace containing multiple discrete event system models.

Author:
Helen Bretzke

Constructor Detail

WorkspaceMessage

public WorkspaceMessage(int type,
                        java.lang.String id,
                        int eventType,
                        WorkspacePublisher source,
                        java.lang.String messageText)
Creates a change notification message for the given model type, model id, event type, source and descriptive text.

Parameters:
type - FSM or DISPLAY
id - the model's id, ignored if display changed
eventType - ADD, REMOVE or MODIFY
source - sender of notification
messageText - descriptive message as a string
